| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0316 — Recovery Inhibition (blacklock)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f0e9d9ea-13eb-5b21-8b35-f69190ddabf9"
